            <abstract>
                <p>A miniature illustrating <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3607Miracle"/> typically 
                    with as a sequence of seven episodes/events, showing: first, the two brothers and the Muslim customer gathered around 
                a piece of cloth; second, the Muslim kissing the head of Nazib; third, the Muslim denouncing Nazib to the judge;
                fourth Nazib lying in prison bound at his hands and feet; fifth, <persName ref="PRS4585Georgeo"/> riding on a horse,
                brandishing a weapon, and appearing to the judge; sixth, the judge handing to Nazib his paper 
                of release; and seventh, Nazib entering the church, in which the people are gathered,
                and handing his paper of release to the priest.</p>
                
